    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei sanctissimi. Anno ab incarnatione [eiusdem] domini
                        nostri Iesu Christi millesimo centesimo trigesimo primo, undecimo die
                        intrante mense ianuarii, indicione nona. <rs key="#Churches">Ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries #Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/2001"
                            >Sancti Benedicti</orgName> de cenobio eiusdem <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterii</rs>, qui est constitutum in honorem <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Offersio/donatio #Decima"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2420">Sancte Crucis</orgName> in <rs
                            key="#Villas">villa</rs> qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries #Villas #Decima">Camposyon</placeName>. Ego dompnus
                            <persName
                            key="#Bishops #siblingOf #Offersio/donatio #Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities"
                            >Belinus</persName>, Dei gratia <placeName
                            key="#Bishops #Dioecesis #Mother_churches #Cities #Residences"
                            ref="#places/41">Paduanus</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, pro remedio anime mee successorum et
                        antecessorum meorum, dispono, offero et concedo omnem <rs key="#Decima"
                            >decimam</rs> de tota pertinencia eiusdem ville Camposyoni et in
                        quibuscumque locis vel terris in quibus predictum monasterium habet et
                        possidet in <rs key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches">episcopatu</rs>
                        Paduanensi. Et insuper ubicumque ecclesie vel cenobia monasterii Sancti
                        Benedicti habent domicilium in episcopatu Patavino, ut dictum est, eidem
                        ecclesie offero et concedo et per presentem <rs key="#Offersio/donatio"
                            >cartam de offersionis</rs> in manu dompni <persName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#people/3568">Henrici</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs> factam in supradicto monasterio et cenobio
                        h[a]b[e]ndam confirmo, ut rectores earumdem ecclesiarum a presenti die
                        faciant de ea decima quicquid facere voluerint, sine omni mea et successorum
                        meorum contradicione, ut superius dictum est, pro anime mee remedium et
                        successorum et antecessorum meorum. Et quidem expondeo atque promitto et
                        obligo me meosque successores supradictam offersionem qualiter superius
                        legitur in integrum ab omni homine defensare; quod si defendere non
                        potuerimus auda si de eadem decima aliquid quo ingenio subtrahere
                        quesierimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in duplum</rs> eandem offersionem
                        restituamus, sicut pro tempore fuerit meliorata aut valuerit, sub
                        extimatione in consimili decima. Actum est in <rs key="#Cities">urbe</rs>
                        Padua, in aula <rs key="#Residences">habitationis</rs> eiusdem dompni Belini
                        episcopi. Feliciter. Ego Belinus Paduanus episcopus mea manu. Signa manuum
                        ++ supradicti dompni Belini episcopi, qui hanc cartulam offersionis fieri
                        rogavit, simul cum suo <rs key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities"
                            >advocato</rs>
                        <persName key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities"
                            ><name>Uberto</name></persName> de Pedrata. Rogati autem fuerunt <rs
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio">testes</rs>: <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name>Albertus</name></persName> [de] Patule, <persName
                            key="#Judge #Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Petrus"
                            >Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>, <persName
                            key="#siblingOf #Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                            ><name>Guvalpertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">frater</rs> episcopi, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name>Guvilericus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                            ><name>Aldigerius</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Anselmus"
                            >Anselmus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                                ref="#people/3577">Ionathas</persName> de Angarano, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name>Adelomus</name></persName> et
                        ceteri. </ab>
